data.description: Located in the heart of Aurora's Historic District, Oregon's antique capital, lies a stunning cottage. This dwelling combines old-world charm and contemporary convenience. Updated kitchen with stainless steel gas appliances, dual sinks, refrigerator, and a spacious island. Each bathroom has seen tasteful renovations. For those who like outdoor entertaining, the expansive covered deck is an ideal spot. Oversized, attached, 2 car garage and a large, separate storage room. The inviting front porch even comes with its very own swing. The cozy living and dining area has built-ins. The ADU provides the potential for multi-generational living, an Airbnb option, or a rental for extra income. Note: 3 Beds 2-1/2 Baths total, the main unit has 2 Beds & 1-1/2 Baths, Attached Guest Quarters / ADU has 1 Bed & 1 Bath plus a small kitchen, eating area, and living room with an exterior entrance.
